==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From a compound of [[εὖ]] {{GG|2095}} and [[λόγος]] {{GG|3056}}; 

===Pronunciation===
*εὐλογέω / eulogeō / yoo-log-eh'-o

===Verb===
'''εὐλογέω'''

# to speak well of, that is, (religiously) to bless (thank or invoke a benediction upon, prosper): - bless, praise.

